#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:29 a640d299f9bb4765bc2b89556dadf0cd
msgid "ESP32 和 ESP8266 是否支持中文 SSID？"
msgstr "Do ESP32 and ESP8266 support Chinese SSIDs?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:31 d813d390b164455287219619c12a99d0
msgid "是支持的，使用中需要路由器或者手机的中文编码方式一致。"
msgstr "Yes, they do. During use, the Chinese encoding method of the router or mobile phone must be consistent."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:33 23c27697f8634b4c8bee2cf2a766697d
msgid "示例：路由器中文编码使用 UTF-8 ，设备中文编码使用 UTF-8，设备就可以正确连接中文 SSID 的路由器。"
msgstr "Example: If the router uses UTF-8 for Chinese encoding and the device also uses UTF-8, the device can correctly connect to the router with a Chinese SSID."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:38 60554f86ae01457da3104d07baebc3c9
msgid "[Scan] ESP32 扫描⼀次需要花多长时间？"
msgstr "[Scan] How long does it take for ESP32 to perform one scan?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:40 7fb7c50e7cc9435b9369e2166dfa61ae
msgid "扫描花费的总时间取决于:"
msgstr "The total time required for scanning depends on:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:42 b49f21981d0b4411961651e0a88862b7
msgid "是被动扫描还是主动扫描，默认为主动扫描。"
msgstr "Whether passive scanning or active scanning is used. The default is active scanning."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:43 3d14e95dc59344059d6a9043adbc7bdf
msgid "每个信道停留的时间，默认主动扫描为 120 ms，被动扫描为 360 ms。"
msgstr "The dwell time on each channel. The default is 120 ms for active scanning and 360 ms for passive scanning."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:44 7802182a01654334b54e9db4e13e1388
msgid "国家码与配置的信道范围，默认为 1~13 信道。"
msgstr "The country code and configured channel range. The default channel range is channels 1~13."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:45 d539260685724be884e73c5586f66933
msgid "是快速扫描还是全信道扫描，默认为快速扫描。"
msgstr "Whether fast scanning or all-channel scanning is used. The default is fast scanning."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:46 19bc999d99cf40ba9ba2a08dc1212ba2
msgid "Station 模式还是 Station-AP 模式，当前是否有连接。"
msgstr "Whether it is in Station mode or Station-AP mode, and whether it is currently connected."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:48 2f4afeb2525946aa9fd1da1ab1738d0d
msgid "默认情况下，1~11 信道为主动扫描，12〜13 信道为被动扫描。"
msgstr "By default, channels 1~11 use active scanning, and channels 12~13 use passive scanning."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:50 56c2cb882a374db2add9e2dfb48251c2
msgid "在 Station 模式没有连接的情况下，全信道扫描总时间为：11*120 + 2*360 = 2040 ms；"
msgstr "When there is no connection in Station mode, the total time for all-channel scanning is: 11*120 + 2*360 = 2040 ms;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:51 3a386bea2d614cf5addf76c4fbeb89d2
msgid "在 Station 模式有连接，或者 Station-AP 模式下，全信道扫描总时间为：11*120 + 2*360 + 13*30 = 2430 ms。"
msgstr "When Station mode is connected, or in Station-AP mode, the total time for all-channel scanning is: 11*120 + 2*360 + 13*30 = 2430 ms."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:56 18300c3dcf4c4ceaa26c00a7a3a2bd0b
msgid "[Scan] 乐鑫是否支持 boundary scans(边界扫描)？"
msgstr "[Scan] Does Espressif support boundary scans?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:58 5c8c61ab211f4f229d8613b80c4074cf
msgid "ESP32 不⽀持 boundary scan。"
msgstr "ESP32 does not support boundary scan."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:63 bebf3c3d2ee247a1ab662bdb566200a9
msgid "客户⾃研产品如何优化⼆次谐波等杂散？"
msgstr "How can customers optimize spurious emissions such as second harmonics in self-developed products?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:65 e84c6c5d5d8e46fca8ee495cbeb8ee56
msgid "⼆次谐波主要来源于射频链路路辐射和 PA 电源辐射，同时易易受到客户底板（板⼦尺⼨）及产品整机影响。因此有如下建议："
msgstr "Second harmonics mainly come from RF link radiation and PA power supply radiation, and are also easily affected by the customer’s baseboard (board size) and the complete product. Therefore, the following suggestions are provided:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:67 2eaaab7a87a84c98a7ec5046b4b02bc7
msgid "在射频匹配中使⽤ ⼀个接近 2.4 pF ⼤⼩的对地电容，可较好地优化射频链路路上的杂散辐射；"
msgstr "Use a shunt capacitor to ground with a value close to 2.4 pF in the RF matching circuit. This can better optimize spurious radiation on the RF link;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:68 d7801a1a859f406cb2dca1da8f67ae22
msgid "在 PA 电源 (芯⽚ 3、4 管脚) ⼊⼝增加⼀个串串联电感可较好减少 PA 电源的杂散辐射。"
msgstr "Add a series inductor at the PA power supply input (chip pins 3 and 4). This can effectively reduce spurious radiation from the PA power supply."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:73 b780769513794882acbee20aaf83643f
msgid "Wi-Fi 信道是什么？可以自行选择信道吗？"
msgstr "What is a Wi-Fi channel? Can I select the channel manually?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:75 5ca572ad476143fea886f78866475695
msgid "信道指的是 Wi-Fi 使用的指定频段中特定频率的波段。不同国家地区使用的信道数是不是同的。⽤户可以参考 `ESP8266 Wi-Fi 信道选择指南 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp8266_wi-fi_channel_selection_guidelines_cn_1.pdf>`_。"
msgstr "A channel refers to a specific frequency band segment within the designated frequency range used by Wi-Fi. The number of channels used varies by country and region. Users can refer to the `ESP8266 Wi-Fi Channel Selection Guide <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp8266_wi-fi_channel_selection_guidelines_cn_1.pdf>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:80 7d9e0d11291d4b9c991e5d9f0cc7b552
msgid "80 MHz 倍频杂散较差该如何解决？"
msgstr "How can poor 80 MHz harmonic spurs be resolved?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:82 7932ca7a5dd742548b98867e5e904c31
msgid "若 80 MHz 倍频杂散超标，如 160 MHz、240 MHz、320 MHz 等均⽐较⾼，可在发送数据 (TXD) 串⼝线路路中串联⼀个阻值约为 470 Ω 的电阻，即可有效抑制 80 MHz 倍频杂散。"
msgstr "If 80 MHz harmonic spurs exceed the limit, such as relatively high spurs at 160 MHz, 240 MHz, 320 MHz, etc., a resistor of about 470 Ω can be connected in series on the transmit data (TXD) UART line to effectively suppress 80 MHz harmonic spurs."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:87 e32c6a44b6b84c9a9e05e2ff49164c35
msgid "[LWIP] 使用 ESP-IDF v4.1，ESP32 用作 SoftAP 模式时如何设置 IP 地址?"
msgstr "[LWIP] When using ESP-IDF v4.1, how do I set the IP address when ESP32 is used in SoftAP mode?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:89 70da09d42b314aa895dc765b47e662e1
msgid "由于 ESP-IDF v4.1 以及以上版本会摒弃掉 TCP/IP 的接口，推荐使用 `ESP-NETIF <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_netif.html>`_ 的接口."
msgstr "Since ESP-IDF v4.1 and later versions deprecate the TCP/IP interface, it is recommended to use the `ESP-NETIF <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_netif.html>`_ interface."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:91 426f60f3f23a4492ac31daf922fd5062
msgid "参考示例代码如下："
msgstr "Reference sample code is as follows:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:119 5fe8267eedc0452c938d75cefb145fab
msgid "[LWIP] ESP32 Station 模式，如何设置静态 IP？"
msgstr "[LWIP] In ESP32 Station mode, how do I set a static IP?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:121 29539554c7a84c6f819ee1341558e42f
msgid "由于 v4.2 以及以上版本会摒弃掉 TCP/IP 的接口，推荐使用 `ESP-NETIF <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_netif.html>`_ 的接口.参考示例代码如下："
msgstr "Since v4.2 and later versions deprecate the TCP/IP interface, it is recommended to use the `ESP-NETIF <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_netif.html>`_ interface. Reference sample code is as follows:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:159 4df01d5a054540cc8313d522b9e8d180
msgid "[LWIP] ESP-IDF 里如何设置 DHCP Server 的 Option 内容？"
msgstr "[LWIP] How do I set DHCP Server Option content in ESP-IDF?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:161 a8dd0757f9ff45bc9d9350f00d778b06
msgid "由于 v4.1 以及以上版本会摒弃掉 tcp/ip 的接口，推荐使用 `ESP-NETIF <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_netif.html>`_ 的接口。DHCP Client 设置方法也可以参考本示例。 参考示例代码如下："
