#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:192 2bd5ed8a314e44eaa6f4653c5aff45e6
msgid "[Performance] 如何测试 Wi-Fi 模组的通信速率？"
msgstr "[Performance] How to test the communication rate of a Wi-Fi module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:194 113d984b82054405b6bbefe735a493ae
msgid "可以使⽤ SDK 中提供的示例 ``example/wifi/iperf`` 中代码进⾏测试。"
msgstr "You can use the code in the example ``example/wifi/iperf`` provided in the SDK for testing."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:199 252012d7f04d4135b40b0e7a6f30c45d
msgid "[LWIP] ESP8266 SoftAP 默认使用哪个网段？"
msgstr "[LWIP] Which network segment does ESP8266 SoftAP use by default?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:201 0a15c2226e764e338977af97f725665b
msgid "ESP8266 SoftAP + Station 模式下, 连接的 192.168.4.X ⽹段时，为什么会失败 ？"
msgstr "In ESP8266 SoftAP + Station mode, why does connection fail when connecting to the 192.168.4.X network segment?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:203 7e8e33037c2f49a99d2ec2f0340cb75e
msgid "ESP8266 SoftAP 默认使用网段 192.168.4.*，IP 地址是 192.168.4.1。ESP8266 如果要连接 192.168.4.X 的路由时，不能分辨是要连接⾃⼰本身的 SoftAp 还是外部路由，所以会造成错误。"
msgstr "ESP8266 SoftAP uses the 192.168.4.* network segment by default, and the IP address is 192.168.4.1. If ESP8266 connects to a router in the 192.168.4.X network segment, it cannot distinguish whether it should connect to its own SoftAP or to the external router, which causes an error."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:208 acaf2c432ba54cbb85264c6980562678
msgid "[Connect] ESP8266 SoftAP 模式支持几个设备？"
msgstr "[Connect] How many devices does ESP8266 SoftAP mode support?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:210 bcce0059c5cf48d98fca719a52bcc7ff
msgid "硬件上最多⽀持 8 个，我们推荐 4 个，这样可以保证模组性能。"
msgstr "The hardware supports up to 8 devices. We recommend 4 devices to ensure module performance."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:215 0918f247bd1d46a185f798652c52b7ce
msgid "ESP8266/ESP32/ESP32-S2 是否支持 web/softAP 配网？"
msgstr "Do ESP8266/ESP32/ESP32-S2 support web/SoftAP provisioning?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:217 ec973de5bab345fb868c2e728558f783
msgid "支持。"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:219 e53f1b80422144e685c2850aa91e521d
msgid "ESP8266 请参考此示例 `ESP8266 softap_prov <https://github.com/espressif/ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/tree/master/examples/provisioning/legacy/softap_prov>`_；"
msgstr "For ESP8266, please refer to this example: `ESP8266 softap_prov <https://github.com/espressif/ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/tree/master/examples/provisioning/legacy/softap_prov>`_;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:220 68b0de1d0e3449eea6a4effab1c6f3f1
msgid "ESP32/ESP32-S2 请参考此示例 `ESP32/ESP32-S2 softap_prov <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/provisioning/legacy/softap_prov>`_。"
msgstr "For ESP32/ESP32-S2, please refer to this example: `ESP32/ESP32-S2 softap_prov <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/provisioning/legacy/softap_prov>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:225 4c7d2b160a994d76b058ff452e73c0c4
msgid "[Connect] ESP8266 和 ESP32 作为 softap 模式如何隐藏 SSID？"
msgstr "[Connect] How can ESP8266 and ESP32 hide the SSID in SoftAP mode?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:227 24655a69838d4db6a0da715415b17eab
msgid "`wifi_ap_config_t <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv416wifi_ap_config_t>`_ 结构体中有一个变量 `ssid_hidden <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html?highlight=hidden#_CPPv4N18wifi_scan_config_t11show_hiddenE>`_，可以设置为隐藏功能。"
msgstr "The `wifi_ap_config_t <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv416wifi_ap_config_t>`_ structure contains a variable `ssid_hidden <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html?highlight=hidden#_CPPv4N18wifi_scan_config_t11show_hiddenE>`_, which can be set to enable SSID hiding."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:232 940b0dde480b42b7950c09c5cb8be1fa
msgid "`esp_wifi_802.11_tx <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-sdk/en/latest/api-reference/wifi/esp_wifi.html?highlight=esp_wifi_802.11_tx#_CPPv417esp_wifi_80211_tx16wifi_interface_tPKvib>`_ 接口中的 buffer 参数中包括 FCS 吗？"
msgstr "Does the buffer parameter in the `esp_wifi_802.11_tx <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-sdk/en/latest/api-reference/wifi/esp_wifi.html?highlight=esp_wifi_802.11_tx#_CPPv417esp_wifi_80211_tx16wifi_interface_tPKvib>`_ API include FCS?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:234 560d6bcb79bd45639ec21bdf899623f1
msgid "不包括， FCS 帧是硬件自动生成的。"
msgstr "No. The FCS frame is automatically generated by hardware."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:239 1d4a0e5fae3e41b09108b36d6fd47137
msgid "ESP-WROOM-32D 支持的 Wi-Fi 频段信息和功率表分别是什么？"
msgstr "What are the Wi-Fi frequency band information and power table supported by ESP-WROOM-32D?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:241 d182f5f0f4a14b5399d34e15ce59339f
msgid "Wi-Fi 频段是 2412 ~ 2484 MHz，软件里可配置可用信道和对应的工作频率。功率表有默认值，也可支持软件配置。详细指导请参考 `《ESP32 Phy Init Bin 重要参数配置说明》 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_phy_init_bin_parameter_configuration_guide_cn.pdf>`_。"
msgstr "The Wi-Fi frequency band is 2412 ~ 2484 MHz. Available channels and their corresponding operating frequencies can be configured in software. The power table has default values and also supports software configuration. For detailed guidance, please refer to `ESP32 Phy Init Bin Parameter Configuration Guide <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_phy_init_bin_parameter_configuration_guide_cn.pdf>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:246 b4a88f8713354c178089b8c41a593c46
msgid "ESP32 Wi-Fi RF 功率最高值是多少？"
msgstr "What is the maximum Wi-Fi RF power of ESP32?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:248 082adbda09074e4fa9e1dc8904263167
msgid "ESP32 RF 功率为 20 dB，即模组最大值。"
msgstr "The ESP32 RF power is 20 dB, which is the maximum value of the module."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:253 245a7690a41240f6a338e21c9a9f62de
msgid "ESP32 如何调整 Wi-Fi 的发射功率？"
msgstr "How to adjust the Wi-Fi transmit power of ESP32?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:255 3e90fb4d463c4fdcb9f7836132fdaf62
msgid "可通过 menuconfig 配置 Component config -> PHY -> Max Wi-Fi TX power(dBm) 来调整 Wi-Fi 的发射功率，最大是 20 dB。"
msgstr "You can adjust the Wi-Fi transmit power through menuconfig: Component config -> PHY -> Max Wi-Fi TX power(dBm). The maximum value is 20 dB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:256 6f5397c76f6c4ef38b2eb41c38f5af47
msgid "或者使用 API `esp_err_t esp_wifi_set_max_tx_power(int8_t power);` 设置调整。"
msgstr "Or use the API `esp_err_t esp_wifi_set_max_tx_power(int8_t power);` to configure it."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:261 c93e0a698b4747dbbb4129ec9ef9e191
msgid "[Connect] ESP32 AP 模式最多支持多少设备连接？"
msgstr "[Connect] How many devices can ESP32 AP mode support at most?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:263 4701df0ef5c54304b7200d4573d293dd
msgid "ESP32 AP 模式，最多可配置为支持 10 个设备连接，默认配置为支持 4 设备。"
msgstr "In ESP32 AP mode, it can be configured to support up to 10 connected devices. The default configuration supports 4 devices."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:268 aab3521c203d4626a18780cf326bc3e8
msgid "[Connect] Wi-Fi 模组如何通过 RSSI 数值划分信号强度等级？"
msgstr "[Connect] How can Wi-Fi modules classify signal strength levels by RSSI values?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:270 4043d81a2acd4c168655f07d2a1ac034
msgid "我们没有对 RSSI 信号强度进行等级划分。如果您需要标准进行划分，可以参考安卓系统的计算方法。"
msgstr "We do not classify RSSI signal strength into levels. If you need a standard classification method, you can refer to the calculation method used in Android."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:296 2370e7db04944eafb4030722e6ca4512
msgid "[Connect] ESP32 做 soft-AP 时为什么会把 STA 踢掉？"
msgstr "[Connect] Why does ESP32 kick off the STA when working as a SoftAP?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:298 9b52045f16b849e09cf75ce92e02196c
msgid "默认情况下连续 5 min 收不到 STA 发过来的数据包就会把 STA 踢掉。该时间可以通过 `esp_wifi_set_inactive_time <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv426esp_wifi_set_inactive_time16wifi_interface_t8uint16_t>`_ 进行修改。"
msgstr "By default, if no packets are received from the STA for 5 consecutive minutes, the STA will be kicked off. This time can be modified through `esp_wifi_set_inactive_time <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv426esp_wifi_set_inactive_time16wifi_interface_t8uint16_t>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:300 b9e2b2f5a29a4a04b1715d1766789ace
msgid "注: esp_wifi_set_inactive_time 新增的 API。"
msgstr "Note: esp_wifi_set_inactive_time is a newly added API."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:302 cd387c8f5abf4cfebe5e3b255256014d
msgid "master commit: ``63b566eb27da187c13f9b6ef707ab3315da24c9d``"
msgstr "master commit: ``63b566eb27da187c13f9b6ef707ab3315da24c9d``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:303 2e31ee8c32794738a67c2e481c330008
msgid "4.2 commit: ``d0dae5426380f771b0e192d8ccb051ce5308485e``"
msgstr "4.2 commit: ``d0dae5426380f771b0e192d8ccb051ce5308485e``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:304 cc8b19d64ff74eb884f6bbd34dcb8e56
msgid "4.1 commit: ``445635fe45b7205497ad81289c5a808156a43539``"
msgstr "4.1 commit: ``445635fe45b7205497ad81289c5a808156a43539``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:305 bf563f0b41ce4623a9a19521e5cb1f12
msgid "4.0 commit: MR 未合, 待定"
msgstr "4.0 commit: MR not merged, TBD"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:306 2b8ff2ef518544c49b657a28842a47a1
msgid "3.3 commit: ``908938bc3cd917edec2ed37a709a153182d511da``"
msgstr "3.3 commit: ``908938bc3cd917edec2ed37a709a153182d511da``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:311 42337abd8dbe4f7a991240f387a7f4bd
msgid "[Connect] ESP32 进行 Wi-Fi 连接时，如何通过错误码判断失败原因？"
msgstr "[Connect] When ESP32 connects to Wi-Fi, how can the failure reason be determined by the error code?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:313 78f03cbb7d7b40c0b8cc86bba0605539
msgid "ESP-IDF v4.0 及以上版本可参考如下代码获取 Wi-Fi 连接失败的原因："
msgstr "For ESP-IDF v4.0 and later, you can refer to the following code to obtain the reason for Wi-Fi connection failure:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:324 d05afd4eb94e4d6c8a6ccb17d56930ab
msgid "当回调函数接收到 ``WIFI_EVENT_STA_DISCONNECTED`` 事件时，可以通过结构体 `wifi_event_sta_disconnected_t <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv429wifi_event_sta_disconnected_t>`_ 的变量 ``reason`` 获取到失败原因。"
msgstr "When the callback function receives the ``WIFI_EVENT_STA_DISCONNECTED`` event, you can obtain the failure reason through the ``reason`` variable of the `wifi_event_sta_disconnected_t <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv429wifi_event_sta_disconnected_t>`_ structure."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:326 5c5a6c1215ff4c8e92bf158fe1af4fc9
msgid "``WIFI_REASON_AUTH_EXPIRE`` 在连接的 auth 阶段，STA 发送了 auth，但在规定时间内未收到 AP 的 auth 回复，有较低概率会出现。"
msgstr "``WIFI_REASON_AUTH_EXPIRE`` occurs during the auth phase of connection. The STA has sent auth, but does not receive the AP's auth response within the specified time. This occurs with a low probability."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:328 e9b86d3641dd4021a87c9caac9e9fd83
msgid "``WIFI_REASON_AUTH_LEAVE`` 通常是由 AP 因为某种原因断开了 STA 连接，reason code 是由 AP 发过来的。"
msgstr "``WIFI_REASON_AUTH_LEAVE`` is usually caused by the AP disconnecting the STA for some reason. The reason code is sent by the AP."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:330 cb8f62963c774d80bb9fcb421adf6b5b
msgid "``WIFI_REASON_4WAY_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` 或者 ``WIFI_REASON_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` 失败原因为密码错误。"
msgstr "``WIFI_REASON_4WAY_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` or ``WIFI_REASON_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` indicates that the failure reason is an incorrect password."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:332 7716dc4809f84d6d9dfddc14136c6905
msgid "其中，``WIFI_REASON_4WAY_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` 为标准通用的错误码，而 ``WIFI_REASON_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` 为自定义错误码。两者区别在于 ``WIFI_REASON_4WAY_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` 为路由器在密码错误时告知设备，产生的错误，``WIFI_REASON_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` 为路由器在密码错误时不告知设备，由设备本身超时机制产生的错误。"
msgstr "Among them, ``WIFI_REASON_4WAY_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` is a standard common error code, while ``WIFI_REASON_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` is a custom error code. The difference is that ``WIFI_REASON_4WAY_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` is generated when the router notifies the device of an incorrect password, while ``WIFI_REASON_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT`` is generated by the device's own timeout mechanism when the router does not notify the device of an incorrect password."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:334 bf6d0f69977249a8a414a5e7b847ed61
msgid "``WIFI_REASON_CONNECTION_FAIL`` 扫描阶段返回的错误码，主要是由于 STA 扫描到了匹配的 AP，但是这个 AP 在黑名单里。AP 在黑名单里面的原因是上次 AP 主动踢掉了 STA，或者 STA 连接 AP 的过程中失败了。"
msgstr "``WIFI_REASON_CONNECTION_FAIL`` is an error code returned during the scan phase. It is mainly because the STA found a matching AP, but this AP is in the blacklist. The AP may be in the blacklist because it actively kicked off the STA last time, or because the STA failed while connecting to the AP."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:339 7c82c8598c0644afbfc40f7502ca0f6c
msgid "ESP32 系列芯片每次连接服务器都会执行域名解析吗？"
msgstr "Do ESP32 series chips perform domain name resolution every time they connect to a server?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:341 a5f22eff41254e8ab7d072b82b25d3b0
msgid "在协议栈内，域名会通过 DNS 进行解析，解析后的数据会在时效内进行缓存。缓存时间基于从 DNS 服务器获取的 TTL 数据，该数据是配置域名时填入的参数，通常为 10 分钟。"
msgstr "In the protocol stack, domain names are resolved through DNS, and the resolved data is cached within its valid period. The cache time is based on the TTL data obtained from the DNS server. This data is a parameter entered when configuring the domain name, and is usually 10 minutes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:346 2faf2f890890441ba12d0ae6d0ef4a00
msgid "[Connect] Wi-Fi Log 中状态机切换后面数字的含义？"
msgstr "[Connect] What do the numbers after state-machine transitions in Wi-Fi logs mean?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:348 0565c025971d4607af10a79d4f2842a3
msgid "eg: run -> init (fc0)，fc0 含义为 STA 收到了 deauth 帧，reason 为密码错误。"
msgstr "eg: run -> init (fc0). fc0 means that the STA received a deauth frame, and the reason is an incorrect password."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:350 20009af5ee064080a88b4e8853e25f73
msgid "c0 代表收到的帧类型（00 代表超时）"
msgstr "c0 represents the received frame type (00 represents timeout)"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:351 1914d41e052640968d0b05bbd76a9322
msgid "f 代表 reason"
msgstr "f represents the reason"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:353 86c6a06c0a9249218d742115859d80ca
msgid "帧类型: [a0 disassoc]、[b0 auth]、[c0 deauth]。"
msgstr "Frame types: [a0 disassoc], [b0 auth], [c0 deauth]."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:358 b08164107df047b7a1ed98b4b5ff34d9
msgid "[Connect] bcn_timeout, ap_probe_send_start 是什么意思？"
msgstr "[Connect] What do bcn_timeout and ap_probe_send_start mean?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:360 6ae9a5aaf1a9481382f4304b97da5122
msgid "在规定时间内（ESP32 默认 6 s，即 60 个 Beacon Interval），STA 未收到 Beacon 帧。 造成该现象可能有:"
msgstr "The STA does not receive a Beacon frame within the specified time (ESP32 default is 6 s, i.e., 60 Beacon Intervals). Possible causes include:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:363 f0622939f49746718e03182cb5c9b1f8
msgid "内存不足。\"ESP32_WIFI_MGMT_SBUF_NUM\" 不够 (log 中会打出 \"esf_buf: t=8, l=beacon_len, ...\" 这样的 Error)。内存不够，可在收到 disconnect event 时打出 heap 大小来排查。"
msgstr "Insufficient memory. \"ESP32_WIFI_MGMT_SBUF_NUM\" is insufficient (the log will print errors such as \"esf_buf: t=8, l=beacon_len, ...\"). If memory is insufficient, you can print the heap size when receiving the disconnect event for troubleshooting."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:364 91a1d3c344d442adbaf59a310e591768
msgid "AP 未发出 beacon。可通过抓包 AP 的 beacon 来排查。"
msgstr "The AP does not send beacon frames. You can capture the AP's beacon packets for troubleshooting."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:365 2a690eb9d83f46f680c8c611f75198b4
msgid "Rssi 值太低。在复杂环境下 Rssi 值较低时，可能导致 STA 收不到 beacon，可通过调用 ``esp_wifi_sta_get_ap_info`` 获取 Rssi 值来排查。"
msgstr "RSSI is too low. In complex environments, a low RSSI value may cause the STA to fail to receive beacon frames. You can call ``esp_wifi_sta_get_ap_info`` to obtain the RSSI value for troubleshooting."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:366 911099f9cab1407ca619160f6de32207
msgid "硬件原因。收包性能差。"
msgstr "Hardware reasons. Poor packet receiving performance."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:368 8d5b816f0c0443529a141d0b40a692c0
msgid "出现 bcn_timeout 时，STA 会尝试发送 5 次 Probe Request，如果 AP 回 Probe Reponse，就保持连接；如果 AP 未回复，STA 发送 Disconnect 事件，并断开连接。"
msgstr "When bcn_timeout occurs, the STA attempts to send 5 Probe Requests. If the AP replies with a Probe Response, the connection is maintained. If the AP does not reply, the STA sends a Disconnect event and disconnects."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:373 4df546754e9741718936ea25f1678a59
msgid "[Connect] Wi-Fi 连接断开后如何重连？"
msgstr "[Connect] How to reconnect after the Wi-Fi connection is disconnected?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:375 25da568ed9274b4fbd8aae0a3d1719c6
msgid "收到 ``WIFI_EVENT_STA_DISCONNECTED`` 之后调用 `esp_wifi_connect <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv416esp_wifi_connectv>`_。"
msgstr "After receiving ``WIFI_EVENT_STA_DISCONNECTED``, call `esp_wifi_connect <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv416esp_wifi_connectv>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:380 a7f052e16c764272b6363b117a55ea24
msgid "[Connect] ESP32 作为 station 时什么时候会把 SoftAP 踢掉？"
msgstr "[Connect] When ESP32 works as a station, when will it kick off the SoftAP?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:382 1a9722b88ad24c43959edc03039d5f46
msgid "默认情况下 6 s 未收到 AP 的 beacon 就会把 AP 踢掉。该时间可以通过 `esp_wifi_set_inactive_time <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv426esp_wifi_set_inactive_time16wifi_interface_t8uint16_t>`_ 进行修改。"
msgstr "By default, if no beacon from the AP is received for 6 s, the AP will be kicked off. This time can be modified through `esp_wifi_set_inactive_time <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_wifi.html#_CPPv426esp_wifi_set_inactive_time16wifi_interface_t8uint16_t>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:387 6267c3faf052423caa34a3691076b9cc
msgid "[Scan] 为什么有时候扫描不到 AP？"
msgstr "[Scan] Why can the AP sometimes not be scanned?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:389 1823be76c1004ef9966976901dfcd932
msgid "常见的原因是 AP 离 STA 太远，也有可能是 scan 的参数配置不恰当导致。"
msgstr "Common causes are that the AP is too far from the STA, or that the scan parameters are not configured properly."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:394 af50a828e7ba40f5af6acadcedc09900
msgid "[Scan] 最多能够扫描多少个 AP？"
msgstr "[Scan] What is the maximum number of APs that can be scanned?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:396 44ef7f8e2f904a5b9e80fbd58e6ff2c2
msgid "能够扫描到的 AP 最大个数没有限制，取决于扫描时周边 AP 的数目与扫描参数的配置，比如每个信道停留的时间，停留时间越长越可能找到全部的 AP。"
msgstr "There is no limit on the maximum number of APs that can be scanned. It depends on the number of surrounding APs during scanning and the scan parameter configuration, such as the dwell time on each channel. The longer the dwell time, the more likely all APs can be found."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:401 8ad5f15a42ac4343bca46d2bf1fffc08
msgid "[Scan] 连接时周围存在多个相同 ssid/password 时能否选出最佳 AP 连接？"
msgstr "[Scan] When multiple APs with the same SSID/password exist nearby during connection, can the best AP be selected for connection?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:403 9bc6862fc5dd481b85ab63d6ff3f3efd
msgid "默认情况下为 WIFI_FAST_SCAN, 总是连接第一个扫描到的 AP。如果要连接最佳AP，需要在设置 station 时将 scan_method 配置成 WIFI_ALL_CHANNEL_SCAN，同时配置 sort_method 来决定选择 RSSI 最强或者是最安全的 AP。"
msgstr "By default, WIFI_FAST_SCAN is used, and the device always connects to the first scanned AP. If you want to connect to the best AP, you need to configure scan_method as WIFI_ALL_CHANNEL_SCAN when setting the station, and configure sort_method to determine whether to select the AP with the strongest RSSI or the highest security."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:408 e441c4f8622e4b929d90337a9e7c37ee
msgid "[Scan] wifi_sta_config_t 中 scan_method 怎么配置？全信道扫描和快速扫描的区别在哪里？"
msgstr "[Scan] How to configure scan_method in wifi_sta_config_t? What is the difference between all-channel scan and fast scan?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:410 2e9848f47ec5415cbe6591d31bdacc6b
msgid "全信道扫描和快速扫描是用在连接前寻找合适 AP 所需要的，scan_method 设定了 fast_scan，可以配合 threshold 来过滤信号或加密方式不强的 AP。"
msgstr "All-channel scan and fast scan are used to find a suitable AP before connection. When scan_method is set to fast_scan, it can work with threshold to filter out APs with weak signals or weak encryption methods."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:412 f7992f76c3e24caeaa8fa01abeaa6683
msgid "选择了 fast_scan 会在扫描到第一个匹配的 AP 的情况下停止扫描，然后进行连接，节省连接的时间。"
msgstr "If fast_scan is selected, scanning stops when the first matching AP is found, and then the device connects to it, saving connection time."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:413 b963efe7276f44969667b2ae1c2b4262
msgid "选择了 all_channel_scan 的时候扫描会进行全信道扫描，然后根据 sort_method 中设定的排序方法，存储四个信号最好或者加密方式最安全的 AP，等到扫描结束后选择其中信号最好或者加密方式最安全的 AP 进行连接。"
msgstr "If all_channel_scan is selected, scanning is performed on all channels. Then, based on the sorting method set in sort_method, four APs with the best signal or highest security are stored. After scanning is complete, the AP with the best signal or highest security among them is selected for connection."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:418 c76437bf9dd6458b983d958d81c19adb
msgid "[LWIP] 如何获取 socket 的错误码？"
msgstr "[LWIP] How to obtain the error code of a socket?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:420 f5beb370b7a34fb0965482a5371f37b3
msgid "ESP-IDF v4.0 版本以上(含v4.0) 标准的做法是 socket API 返回失败后直接通过 `errno` 的值来获取错误码。"
msgstr "For ESP-IDF v4.0 and later versions (including v4.0), the standard method is to obtain the error code directly through the value of `errno` after the socket API returns failure."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:421 435aa98d90c04c5e8b9540e6eff9a3c5
msgid "ESP-IDF v4.0 版本以下标准的做法是 socket API 返回失败后调用 `getsockopt(sockfd, SOL_SOCKET, SO_ERROR, …)` 的方式获取错误码，否则当多个 socket 并行操作的时候可能会获取到不正确的错误码。"
msgstr "For ESP-IDF versions earlier than v4.0, the standard method is to call `getsockopt(sockfd, SOL_SOCKET, SO_ERROR, …)` after the socket API returns failure to obtain the error code. Otherwise, when multiple sockets operate in parallel, an incorrect error code may be obtained."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:426 b5ab7982e23f4a3d9fac62361879f804
msgid "[LWIP] 默认 TCP keep-alive 时间为多少？"
msgstr "[LWIP] What is the default TCP keep-alive time?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:428 fb2682a0a9984816ab5b589014cec0ef
msgid "默认情况下，如果连续两个小时收不到任何 TCP 报文，会每隔 75 秒发送一个 TCP keep-alive 报文，连续发送 9 个 tcp keep-alive 报文，如果依然收不到对方发过来的任何报文 LWIP 会断开 TCP 连接。"
msgstr "By default, if no TCP packets are received for two consecutive hours, a TCP keep-alive packet is sent every 75 seconds. If 9 TCP keep-alive packets are sent consecutively and no packets are still received from the peer, LWIP disconnects the TCP connection."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:430 7929f9608bc14fecaf3863b2353de6f8
msgid "Keep-alive 可通过 socket option 进行配置。"
msgstr "Keep-alive can be configured through socket options."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:435 92c7976732fa47ff94eff308f5176739
msgid "[LWIP] TCP 重传间隔？"
msgstr "[LWIP] What is the TCP retransmission interval?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:437 6ca81a249fb84668b06eaaae35d3c759
msgid "ESP32 作为发送方时，默认情况下，首次重传通常在 2 ~ 3 秒左右, 之后依据 Jacoboson 算法决定下次重传间隔，重传间隔可以简单地理解为 2 的倍数递增。"
msgstr "When ESP32 acts as the sender, by default, the first retransmission usually occurs after about 2 ~ 3 seconds. Subsequent retransmission intervals are determined according to the Jacobson algorithm, and can be simply understood as increasing by multiples of 2."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:442 925003e8e73c4a1d82e0ecb687910360
msgid "[LWIP] 最多能够创建多少个 socket ？"
msgstr "[LWIP] How many sockets can be created at most?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:444 2672678797d04905b612e2378c7845a5
msgid "最多 32 个，默认为 10 个。"
msgstr "Up to 32 sockets can be created, and the default is 10."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:449 42350bbf4f624c6f938e4fcd4fcd3ce1
msgid "[Sleep] ESP32 有哪几种休眠方式及其区别是什么？"
msgstr "[Sleep] What sleep modes does ESP32 have and what are their differences?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:451 7198e5fcdb5343a7b6fc19d10ed551c3
msgid "一共有三种休眠方式: Modem sleep, Light sleep 和 Deep sleep。"
msgstr "There are three sleep modes in total: Modem sleep, Light sleep, and Deep sleep."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:453 3b8769980af949f792628730c1b50e0f
msgid "Modem sleep: WiFi 协议规定的 station WMM 休眠方式(station 发送 NULL 数据帧通知 AP 休眠或醒来)，station 连接上 AP 之后自动开启，进入休眠状态后关闭射频模块，休眠期间保持和 AP 的连接，station 断开连接后 modem sleep 不工作。ESP32 modem sleep 进入休眠状态后还可以选择降低 CPU 时钟频率，进一步降低电流。"
msgstr "Modem sleep: A station WMM sleep mode defined by the Wi-Fi protocol. The station sends NULL data frames to notify the AP that it is sleeping or awake. It is automatically enabled after the station connects to the AP. After entering sleep state, the RF module is turned off. During sleep, the connection with the AP is maintained. Modem sleep does not work after the station disconnects. After ESP32 enters modem sleep, you can also choose to reduce the CPU clock frequency to further reduce current consumption."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:454 2c5db2e23309405488c0aed223d15a86
msgid "Light sleep: 基于 modem sleep 的 station 休眠方式，和 modem sleep 的不同之处在于进入休眠状态后不仅关闭射频模块，还暂停 CPU，退出休眠状态后 CPU 从断点处继续运行。"
msgstr "Light sleep: A station sleep mode based on modem sleep. Unlike modem sleep, after entering sleep state, it not only turns off the RF module, but also pauses the CPU. After exiting sleep, the CPU continues running from the point where it stopped."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:455 fac2933bf06e4a45a50fb84373d70040
msgid "Deep sleep: 非 WiFi 协议规定的休眠方式，进入休眠状态后关闭除 RTC 模块外的所有其他模块，退出休眠状态后整个系统重新运行(类似于系统重启)，休眠期间不能保持和 AP 的连接。"
msgstr "Deep sleep: A sleep mode not defined by the Wi-Fi protocol. After entering sleep state, all modules except the RTC module are turned off. After exiting sleep, the entire system restarts (similar to a system reboot). During sleep, the connection with the AP cannot be maintained."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:460 c07238cc883847978d461ee362e33cd3
msgid "[Sleep] ESP32 modem sleep 降频功能在哪打开？"
msgstr "[Sleep] Where can the ESP32 modem sleep frequency-reduction function be enabled?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:462 301e031322b14ae8b2c70d8964d29f83
msgid "在 menuconfig -> Component Config -> Power Management 中打开。"
msgstr "Enable it in menuconfig -> Component Config -> Power Management."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:467 f70d30e624c64e37a3c2d9a1065bc0ef
msgid "[Sleep] ESP32 modem sleep 降频功能最低能降到多少？"
msgstr "[Sleep] What is the lowest frequency that ESP32 modem sleep frequency reduction can reach?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:469 761c3c2417e54b3381c480c56f193171
msgid "目前 CPU 时钟最低能降到 40 MHz。"
msgstr "Currently, the CPU clock can be reduced to as low as 40 MHz."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:474 76b7312a76c14953b38b8b4df29599a5
msgid "[Sleep] ESP32 modem sleep 平均电流大小影响因素？"
msgstr "[Sleep] What factors affect the average current of ESP32 modem sleep?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:476 b84de96a06584093b7a139702bc4630d
msgid "ESP32 modem sleep 平均电流大小与 CPU 单核还是双核，CPU 时钟频率，CPU 空闲时间比，测试过程中 Wi-Fi 是否有数据收发，数据收发频率，射频模块发射功率，测试路由器发送 beacon 时间点是否准确，是否有外设模块工作等因素有关。"
msgstr "The average current of ESP32 modem sleep is related to factors such as whether the CPU is single-core or dual-core, CPU clock frequency, CPU idle-time ratio, whether Wi-Fi data is transmitted or received during the test, data transmission/reception frequency, RF module transmit power, whether the test router sends beacons at accurate timing points, and whether peripheral modules are working."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:481 efdb86e1d39a4472a13907cca56c27f6
msgid "[Sleep] 为什么测到的 modem sleep 平均电流偏高？"
msgstr "[Sleep] Why is the measured modem sleep average current too high?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:483 e01600f8ec824bdb92fc03bd4102d0c8
msgid "测试过程中有较多的 Wi-Fi 数据收发。数据收发越多，进入休眠状态的机会越少，平均电流就越高。"
msgstr "There is a large amount of Wi-Fi data transmission/reception during the test. The more data is transmitted or received, the fewer chances the device has to enter sleep mode, and the higher the average current will be."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:484 d56dc2324f37454da20e7b06f87cc7c6
msgid "测试用的路由器发送 beacon 时间点不准确。Station 需要定时醒来监听 beacon，若 beacon 时间点不准确，station 会等待较长时间，进入休眠状态的时间就越少，平均电流就越高。"
msgstr "The test router does not send beacons at accurate timing points. The station needs to wake up periodically to listen for beacons. If the beacon timing is inaccurate, the station will wait for a longer time, resulting in less time spent in sleep mode and higher average current."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:485 6df1458f0785425cacc8f736e9f3be5b
msgid "测试过程中有外设模块在工作，请关闭外设模块再进行测试。"
msgstr "Peripheral modules are working during the test. Please disable peripheral modules before testing."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:486 5cdfaad860ef4b4a86ae248f3204fcdd
msgid "开启了 station + softap 模式，modem sleep 只在 station only 模式下才会降低电流。"
msgstr "Station + SoftAP mode is enabled. Modem sleep reduces current only in station-only mode."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:491 b84768095c6f44c5a5b6617ec0e067eb
msgid "[Sleep] 为什么测到的 light sleep 平均电流偏高？"
msgstr "[Sleep] Why is the measured light sleep average current too high?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:493 b9eb8db240594b2fac5eebed8ced39cd
msgid "除了上述四个原因之外还可能是："
msgstr "In addition to the four reasons above, it may also be caused by:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:495 f9b924c2992d40b7a21a7b37f78d843f
msgid "应用层代码在不停地运行，CPU 没有机会暂停。"
msgstr "Application-layer code is running continuously, leaving no chance for the CPU to pause."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:496 94b40c06e1bc420e929ad0cf7d50ab0b
msgid "应用层使用了 ets timer 或者 esp timer，且 timer 的超时时间间隔较短，CPU 没有机会暂停。"
msgstr "The application layer uses ets timer or esp timer, and the timer timeout interval is short, leaving no chance for the CPU to pause."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:501 4581b321b9754437922b1eb464c4f733
msgid "ESP8266 是否支持 802.11k/v/r 协议？"
msgstr "Does ESP8266 support the 802.11k/v/r protocols?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:503 2abc858453814c81b6cec7201ea147b5
msgid "当前只支持 802.11k 和 802.11v，可参考示例 `roaming <https://github.com/espressif/ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/tree/master/examples/wifi/roaming>`_。"
msgstr "Currently, only 802.11k and 802.11v are supported. Refer to the example `roaming <https://github.com/espressif/ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/tree/master/examples/wifi/roaming>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:508 0349714299444b0e866c34e174f26dbc
msgid "[Connect] NONOS_SDK `2.1.0` 升级到 `2.2.2` 后，连接时间变长？"
msgstr "[Connect] After upgrading NONOS_SDK from `2.1.0` to `2.2.2`, why does the connection time become longer?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:510 98a1ba5ca850455dbaf8163295b1ee22
msgid "请升级到 NONOS_SDK `master` 版本，该版本中解决了 CCMP 加密与某些 AP 不兼容的问题。"
msgstr "Please upgrade to the NONOS_SDK `master` version. This version resolves the compatibility issue between CCMP encryption and certain APs."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:515 c07cbd45fdf04d439027c82f2b45e0c8
msgid "ESP32 如何收发 Wi-Fi 802.11 数据包？"
msgstr "How does ESP32 transmit and receive Wi-Fi 802.11 packets?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:517 55585b5ddaf54b7b9e4b65cd78074e5c
msgid "可以通过如下 API 进行 802.11 数据包收发："
msgstr "802.11 packets can be transmitted and received through the following APIs:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:524 63f96fbfffb44009b90b89f94b09a593
msgid "上述 API 在 MDF 项目中有用到，可以参考：`mconfig_chain <https://github.com/espressif/esp-mdf/blob/master/components/mconfig/mconfig_chain.c>`_。"
msgstr "The above APIs are used in the MDF project. Refer to: `mconfig_chain <https://github.com/espressif/esp-mdf/blob/master/components/mconfig/mconfig_chain.c>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:529 5045d8e95d0c49748dfe4f38705094d6
msgid "[Connect] ESP32 系列 & ESP8266 路由器连接失败有哪些可能原因？"
msgstr "[Connect] What are the possible reasons for ESP32 series & ESP8266 router connection failures?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:531 e29adac66f13475b8d45778506485766
msgid "检查配置中的 SSID 与 Password 是否正确。"
msgstr "Check whether the SSID and Password in the configuration are correct."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:532 652cecb03ef74eb6a4d7a90610408408
msgid "不建议使用中文 SSID，可能存在不同中文编码带来的异常。"
msgstr "Chinese SSIDs are not recommended, as issues may occur due to different Chinese character encodings."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:533 653b2bbf3d934d6d8c53b36db5d6bbc5
msgid "需要注意 bssid_set 的设置，如果不需要指定路由的 MAC 地址，那么需配置 stationConf.bssid_set = 0。"
msgstr "Pay attention to the bssid_set setting. If you do not need to specify the router MAC address, configure stationConf.bssid_set = 0."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:534 c78334828e4e45c18c3c66fd0f10215e
msgid "wifi_config_t wifi_config 建议使用静态变量 `static` 来定义。"
msgstr "It is recommended to define wifi_config_t wifi_config as a static variable using `static`."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:539 70cd7a2caceb40d1b591dd1a78bc00c8
msgid "[Connect] ESP8266 有那些配网方式？"
msgstr "[Connect] What provisioning methods does ESP8266 support?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:541 97c331cdd1a94649a5e1cd1e3c1e68c1
msgid "SmartConfig 模式：⼀键配置⽅式，设备在 sniffer 模式扫描特征包的⽅式。"
msgstr "SmartConfig mode: one-click configuration method, where the device scans characteristic packets in sniffer mode."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:542 2c71432ea444405f85f33f4610bdef5d
msgid "SoftAP 模式：设备开启 SoftAP， ⼿机连接 SoftAP 后建⽴稳定的 TCP/UDP 连接后，发送 SSID 和密码。"
msgstr "SoftAP mode: the device starts SoftAP. After the phone connects to the SoftAP and establishes a stable TCP/UDP connection, it sends the SSID and password."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:543 ef53f40afeb84e8dbe22d91b6329d43c
msgid "WPS 模式：此⽅式需要设备中增加按键；或连接到设备的 SoftAP 后使⽤⼿机软件控制开启 WPS。"
msgstr "WPS mode: this method requires adding a button to the device; or after connecting to the device's SoftAP, use mobile software to enable WPS."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:548 52af9b5d12a64f56b64227c7b98b0053
msgid "[Connect] SmartConfig 配⽹ Wi-Fi 参数信息有哪些要求？"
msgstr "[Connect] What are the requirements for Wi-Fi parameter information in SmartConfig provisioning?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:550 a7c57fcfa8ad49a28e16776621f45e2c
msgid "根据 `wifi spec` 要求，SSID 不超过 32 bytes，Password 不超过 64 bytes。"
msgstr "According to `wifi spec` requirements, the SSID must not exceed 32 bytes, and the Password must not exceed 64 bytes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:555 8866564d363b4d8cbffb9cbfa3677118
msgid "[Connect] ESP8266 Wi-Fi 是否支持 WAP2 企业级加密？"
msgstr "[Connect] Does ESP8266 Wi-Fi support WPA2 Enterprise encryption?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:557 5cf2a96aa6aa46e39c9e8da5136bc6e6
msgid "支持。请参考示例 `wpa2_enterprise <https://github.com/espressif/ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/tree/master/examples/wifi/wpa2_enterprise>`_。"
msgstr "Yes. Refer to the example `wpa2_enterprise <https://github.com/espressif/ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/tree/master/examples/wifi/wpa2_enterprise>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:558 b0dcba26deab41e9b773e150131a1612
msgid "可使用 FreeRADIUS 服务搭建 RADIUS 服务器，请参考 `FreeRADIUS <https://freeradius.org/documentation/>`_。"
msgstr "You can use the FreeRADIUS service to set up a RADIUS server. Refer to `FreeRADIUS <https://freeradius.org/documentation/>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:563 a0e262d97edf4f90a116517653137fd6
msgid "[Connect] ESP32 保持 Wi-Fi 连接的低功耗模式有哪些？"
msgstr "[Connect] What low-power modes can ESP32 use while maintaining Wi-Fi connection?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:565 43b1b038871d4b2a8f0a3af7c038e8e5
msgid "在保存 Wi-Fi 连接的场景中，芯片会在 Active 和 Modem-sleep 模式之间自动切换，功耗也会在两种模式间变化。"
msgstr "In scenarios where Wi-Fi connection is maintained, the chip automatically switches between Active and Modem-sleep modes, and power consumption also changes between these two modes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:566 3ef4b7e3efa0412ba7065b6f32d573e8
msgid "ESP32 支持在 light sleep 下 Wi-Fi 保活，自动唤醒间隔由 DTIM 参数决定。"
msgstr "ESP32 supports Wi-Fi keep-alive in light sleep. The automatic wake-up interval is determined by the DTIM parameter."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:567 1805370576984adea98b1069083c9597
msgid "例程参见：ESP-IDF - > examples - > wifi - > power_save。"
msgstr "Example: ESP-IDF - > examples - > wifi - > power_save."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:572 43b7470a673f443ca219faee34b30c8b
msgid "乐鑫芯片是否支持 WPA3？"
msgstr "Do Espressif chips support WPA3?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:574 2d5f89b304a54ca7b2de520a659aeaa4
msgid "ESP32 系列：esp-idf 从 release/v4.1 版本开始支持 WPA3 ，默认使能，可在 menuconfig > Component config > Wi-Fi 中配置。"
msgstr "ESP32 series: esp-idf supports WPA3 starting from release/v4.1. It is enabled by default and can be configured in menuconfig > Component config > Wi-Fi."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:575 2dffcb81e3a84414b3ae1a94494e807b
msgid "ESP8266：ESP8266_RTOS_SDK 的 master 分支开始支持 WPA3 ，默认使能，可在 menuconfig > Component config > Wi-Fi 中配置。"
msgstr "ESP8266: WPA3 is supported starting from the master branch of ESP8266_RTOS_SDK. It is enabled by default and can be configured in menuconfig > Component config > Wi-Fi."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:580 25f7164c05d84994a33798f6f1bda442
msgid "[Connect] 当环境内存在多个相同 SSID 时，设备如何连接 ？"
msgstr "[Connect] When there are multiple APs with the same SSID in the environment, how does the device connect?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:582 a295524ee5564d5993a79dd9418560a8
msgid "设备会连接优先扫描到的 AP 设备。"
msgstr "The device connects to the AP that is scanned first."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:583 63ea1b20e5ec413fa7c839e7727970b0
msgid "如果想要根据信号质量等排序，可以使用 Scan 方法自主筛选。"
msgstr "If you want to sort APs based on signal quality or other criteria, you can use the Scan method to filter them manually."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:584 f489ea9a06cb48a48ab5406b24bec271
msgid "如果想要连接指定 AP, 可以在连接参数中填入 BSSID 信息。"
msgstr "If you want to connect to a specified AP, you can fill in the BSSID information in the connection parameters."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:589 b6bc2cafbee64263a33f29ba9aa147ea
msgid "[Connect] ESP8266 有中继器方案吗？"
msgstr "[Connect] Is there a repeater solution for ESP8266?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:591 72172687dda64f5eac9801a6dd0291bb
msgid "乐鑫官方未推出中继类应用方案。"
msgstr "Espressif has not officially released a repeater application solution."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:592 b566e02f9d0b4789942f8d04491bb0ee
msgid "社区中有相关中继的应用，可以在 github 中查询，中继速率建议基于实际测试。"
msgstr "There are related repeater applications in the community. You can search on GitHub. The repeater throughput should be evaluated based on actual testing."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:597 e7eafabc6f534ede8e4eb6920e46eea2
msgid "ESP-NOW 是什么？有哪些优势与场景？"
msgstr "What is ESP-NOW? What are its advantages and use cases?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:599 8a1e5b9f35b148b082411cff94b26327
msgid "`ESP-NOW <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_now.html>`_ 是一种由乐鑫公司定义的无连接 Wi-Fi 通信协议。"
msgstr "`ESP-NOW <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/network/esp_now.html>`_ is a connectionless Wi-Fi communication protocol defined by Espressif."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:600 5b8d4d298dfa40288e92b4d032c15773
msgid "在 ESP-NOW 中，应用程序数据被封装在各个供应商的动作帧中，然后在无连接的情况下，从一个 Wi-Fi 设备传输到另一个 Wi-Fi 设备。"
msgstr "In ESP-NOW, application data is encapsulated in vendor-specific action frames and then transmitted from one Wi-Fi device to another without a connection."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:601 8911e8f9d3f447b79d62fecef8d753d1
msgid "ESP-NOW 广泛应用于智能照明、远程控制、传感器等领域。"
msgstr "ESP-NOW is widely used in smart lighting, remote control, sensors, and other fields."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:606 8f9634c4a2ad444cbb6c7f109cbd2526
msgid "ESP32 数据帧和管理帧的重传次数是多少？是否可以配置？"
msgstr "How many retransmissions are used for ESP32 data frames and management frames? Can this be configured?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:608 f24c03851cc34d419b3f865867551087
msgid "重传次数是 31 次，不可以配置。"
msgstr "The number of retransmissions is 31 and cannot be configured."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:613 c1e893e6508e40a2b1455e9d6fdeb5c9
msgid "ESP32 如何自定义 hostname？"
msgstr "How can ESP32 customize the hostname?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:615 574e3b6acbf547dcbb247de21fc7c2b3
msgid "以 ESP-IDF v4.2 为例，可以在 menuconfig > Component Config > LWIP > Local netif hostname，然后输入指定的 hostname 即可。"
msgstr "Taking ESP-IDF v4.2 as an example, you can go to menuconfig > Component Config > LWIP > Local netif hostname, and then enter the specified hostname."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:616 2b92d69426a0413480d4aaa2375b6a91
msgid "不同的版本在命名上可能略有区别。"
msgstr "The naming may differ slightly in different versions."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:621 8e646c8e1c4f4d13a9b1f6220e2ac383
msgid "如何获取 802.11 无线数据包？"
msgstr "How to capture 802.11 wireless packets?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:623 f89e73abb1844d03a363a2d26bb3e3da
msgid "可以参考 ESP-IDF 编程文档中的 `Wireshark 使用指南 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-guides/wireshark-user-guide.html>`_ 。"
msgstr "You can refer to the `Wireshark User Guide <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-guides/wireshark-user-guide.html>`_ in the ESP-IDF Programming Guide."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:628 fea687d491544d48a44ff21fd36e0c98
msgid "ESP32 Wi-Fi 支持 PMF(Protected Management Frames) 和 PFS(Perfect Forward Secrecy) 吗？"
