msgstr "The AP RSSI can be obtained through scanning. Refer to the example `scan <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/wifi/scan>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:638 57f8556186bf430995de8c3ca4da7145
