msgid "不支持， 建议参考 ASD-1148 方式测试。"
msgstr "Not supported. It is recommended to test by referring to the ASD-1148 method."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:673 761b7a314fb34536b57a1bfe564f51ec
msgid "ESP-01S模组支持给摄像头做无线连接，传输视频么?"
msgstr "Does the ESP-01S module support wireless connection for a camera and video transmission?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:674 07b2491e7c10426e8d52bfaf98206e7e
msgid "ESP-01S模组TCP协议传输下速率最大1M左右，若是速率要求不是很高，则可传输。"
msgstr "The maximum rate of the ESP-01S module under TCP protocol transmission is about 1 Mbps. If the rate requirement is not very high, it can transmit video."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:677 0681d795e88b47e0939226833c977db7
msgid "ESP-12S模组出厂固件支持HTTP协议吗？"
msgstr "Does the factory firmware of the ESP-12S module support the HTTP protocol?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:678 85bc29b6d4ba4126b8217ce2f6f4151f
msgid "出厂固件不支持HTTP功能模块AT指令，需要通过TCP协议做打包处理。"
msgstr "The factory firmware does not support HTTP function module AT commands. It needs to be packaged and processed through the TCP protocol."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:681 7fd3e9556b004db0a61f987d6521aa63
msgid "为什么烧写8266乐鑫最新固件发送AT指令无反应"
msgstr "Why is there no response when sending AT commands after flashing the latest Espressif firmware to ESP8266?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:682 75f2bfa33a8a4827a378162e9583901a
msgid "乐鑫最新固件通讯AT口是GPIO13 GPIO15引脚，并非默认串口引脚"
msgstr "The AT communication port of the latest Espressif firmware is GPIO13 and GPIO15, not the default serial port pins."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:685 fbecefdf8b664458aaf17e6d26c2472d
