msgstr "TTL level."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:693 3b2bfa0bd4df48759c8d87f40477eec9
msgid "ESP-12F转接板上的降压芯片型号和三个电阻有什么作用"
msgstr "What are the model of the buck chip and the functions of the three resistors on the ESP-12F adapter board?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:694 61829158d6eb41cb88d836b0766e979d
msgid "降压芯片型号为HT7333，三个电阻分别给模块的使能脚和GPIO15引脚做上下拉使用"
msgstr "The buck chip model is HT7333. The three resistors are used as pull-up and pull-down resistors for the module enable pin and GPIO15 pin."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:697 cf3c02724deb404db8b8d0cd6c668dc8
msgid "ESP-07S模组和ESP-12S模组底部的焊盘是干啥用的"
msgstr "What are the bottom pads of the ESP-07S module and ESP-12S module used for?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:698 fa2870dd282245bbba9bc2664ee9e3ad
msgid "底部焊盘是接地散热的功能，建议焊接的时候焊接上方便模组工作的时候散热"
msgstr "The bottom pads are used for grounding and heat dissipation. It is recommended to solder them during assembly to help dissipate heat when the module is working."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:701 b11cb5dbb68e4c979ed79a0425d0a21e
msgid "8266模组上的LED是做什么用的，为什么不是常亮，常亮的后果是什么"
msgstr "What is the LED on the 8266 module used for? Why is it not always on, and what happens if it stays on?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:702 fdafb9abf2e04c6aa8842c806bc26dee
msgid "LED灯接到芯片的GPIO2引脚，此引脚与UART1的TXD共用，此时上电会输出一下打印信息，所以不是常亮，常亮的后果是模块固件跑飞了"
msgstr "The LED is connected to GPIO2 of the chip. This pin is shared with UART1 TXD. It outputs some log information during power-on, so it is not always on. If it stays on constantly, it means the module firmware has crashed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:705 0816e52b48cd4bcd9799e1e1a5b5b455
msgid "为什么AT MQTT固件，我发送带后缀_CUR或者_DEF这样的指令无法成功"
msgstr "Why do commands with suffixes such as _CUR or _DEF fail when I use AT MQTT firmware?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:706 7f4379b0e3954cf485ee16a4d280ea65
msgid "因为新版本的AT MQTT固件已经取消带后缀的指令，如果需要保存或者不保存相关参数可以使用AT+SYSSTORE指令进行参数存储"
msgstr "Because the new version of the AT MQTT firmware has removed commands with suffixes. If you need to save or not save related parameters, you can use the AT+SYSSTORE command for parameter storage."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:709 bab7441ab8054bc39431742dc06c35f9
msgid "ESP8266模组EspTouch和Airkiss配网困难或者失败应该从哪几个方面排查问题"
msgstr "What aspects should be checked when ESP8266 module EspTouch and Airkiss provisioning is difficult or fails?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:710 037e287d260045228499d4fb86b9c2db
msgid "esptouch 配网失败概率较高的原因通常如下： 1.连接的热点使用人数较多 2.连接的热点信号质量较差 3.路由器不转组播 4.路由器开启了双频合一，手机连接到 5G 频段。"
msgstr "Common reasons for a high failure probability of esptouch provisioning are as follows: 1. Too many users are connected to the hotspot. 2. The signal quality of the connected hotspot is poor. 3. The router does not forward multicast packets. 4. The router has dual-band integration enabled, and the phone is connected to the 5 GHz band."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:717 fea552bc47bd4e4cad5d34daa37d8b08
msgid "WIFI模块出厂是否有密码"
msgstr "Does the Wi-Fi module have a factory default password?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/wifi.rst:718 4547abb716234fe9a7ea2261b1d5e597
msgid "模块默认出厂为AP模式，只有一个开放式的热点，无密码"
msgstr "By default, the module is shipped in AP mode. It only has an open hotspot with no password."

